title: Steven Wilson Royal Albert Hall 2015-09-28 (Stunning HD Videos)
description:
Steven Wilson
September 28, 2015
Royal Albert Hall 
London, UK

Here is a good portion of the first Royal Albert Hall concert taken by a fan with great seats in stunning HD quality.  These videos were posted to YouTube but removed.  This is the parital concert, 6 songs are missing (4 songs from the main set and 2 songs from the encore)   Enjoy!

Songs included:

02 - 3 Years Older
03 - Hand Cannot Erase
04 - Perfect Life
05 - Routine (with Ninet Teyeb)
06 - Home Invasion
08 - Ancestral
09 - Happy Returns
11 - Drag Ropes (Storm Corrosion cover with Mikael Akerfeldt live debut)
12 - Index
13 - How Is Your Life Today- (Porcupine Tree song)
14 - Lazarus (Porcupine Tree song)
15 - My Book of Regrets
16 - Harmony Korine

The full setlist can be found here:
 
http://www.setlist.fm/setlist/steven-wilson/2015/royal-albert-hall-london-england-3bf4dcb4.html
